  "headline": "<h2>Winning Frequency and RTP</h2>",
  "content": "<p>If you're like us, you want your gambling games like you want your carrot cake: profitable and available in 18.12% frequency. Bonus Bunnies delivers on both. With an RTP of 96.14%, players can expect solid returns from this game. And with every fifth spin potentially resulting in a winning combination, your pockets are sure to inflate faster than a bunny hopping on a trampoline.</p><p>Of course, winning big isn't just about the numbers. The game's design and features are sure to keep players entertained as they wait for those elusive lucky spins. Our personal favorite is the bonus round where the bunnies hop around the farm collecting carrots and adding extra rewards to your totals. It's like watching a slow-motion replay of the Easter Bunny delivering candy while high on sugar.</p>"
}

{
